1091
01:25:20,292 --> 01:25:22,434
Medford is a hold harmless district.

1092
01:25:23,615 --> 01:25:29,179
Hold harmless means that we won't get lowered and we won't get raised, except for the minimum aid hit.

1093
01:25:30,000 --> 01:25:40,228
Because of the numbers and because of the economics of the Chapter 70 formula, which places Medford between the wealthy communities and the less wealthy communities.

1094
01:25:40,668 --> 01:25:42,209
At one time, we received as much as 37%

1095
01:25:43,817 --> 01:25:45,978
of our school budget from the state.

1096
01:25:46,558 --> 01:25:53,221
Today, we're lucky to see 19% from the state, at least in the general distribution, maybe even less.

1097
01:25:53,961 --> 01:25:57,442
And it won't move until these things actually take place.

1098
01:25:58,022 --> 01:25:59,343
So that's what hold harmless means.

1099
