1111
01:27:05,151 --> 01:27:06,272
The Senate put it back in.

1112
01:27:06,292 --> 01:27:10,675
The Governor apparently decided that it was worth something.

1113
01:27:12,077 --> 01:27:13,357
I don't know how that's going to play out.

1114
